parameter.description:
The message attributes to send.
    The value should be a string in JSON format.
    ' Eg:
    { attributeName :
        {
             DataType: value,
             StringValue: value
        }
    }'

The message system attributes to send.
    The value should be a string in JSON format.
    'Eg:
    { systemAttributeName :
        {
             DataType: value,
             StringValue: value
        }
    }'
